data.description: Discover your dream home in El Paso! This stunning two-story gem boasts three spacious bedrooms and three total baths, offering both comfort & convenience. Outside, the home's front showcases a charming stucco exterior in a warm palette with cultured stone accents, adding curb appeal. The master bedroom is a sanctuary with a walk-in closet ft. built-in shelving, plush carpeting, and three large windows for abundant natural light. Step into relaxation with a double sink vanity in the master bath, accompanied by a walk-in shower and a bubbly tub. The heart of this home is the beautifully designed kitchen complete with an inviting island w.  granite countertops, perfect for culinary creations, and an adjacent, cozy breakfast area. The living room welcomes you with its high ceilings and freshly cleaned carpeting also. Finally, step into the backyard oasis, where the covered patio awaits its next owner, all sitting within a block of Tom Lea Elementary and a short 10 minute drive to Fort Bliss!
